# This repo (atlas-trading-platform) is scoped to live/, frontend/, and docs/ only -
# pine/, dashboard/, data/, screenshots/, and .claude/ are deliberately not part of it
# (see docs/monorepo-proposal.md, Decision 1). Listed here as a safety net against an
# accidental future `git add -A`/`git add .` pulling them in - the actual commits in
# this repo add live/, frontend/, and docs/ explicitly, not via a wildcard add.
/pine/
/dashboard/
/data/
/screenshots/
/.claude/
